    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Raised ridges across the bound spine of a book indicating the location of the cords beneath the covering material. Distinguished from "cords (binding components)," the twisted strands of fibrous material to which the sections of a book are sewn.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Uitstekende randjes over de rug van een boek, die de plaats aangeven van de koorden onder de omslag. Te onderscheiden van 'touwen (boekbandonderdelen)'; dit zijn gedraaide strengen vezelig materiaal waarop de delen  van een boek zijn vastgenaaid.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052405/Krimpen, Boek (1966)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Erhabene Rippen, die über den gebundenen Buchrücken laufen und die den Verlauf der Heftbänder unter dem Abdeckmaterial markieren. Unterschieden von "Heftbänder (bindende Komponenten)," den gedrehten Strängen aus Fasermaterial, mit denen die Abschnitte eines Buches zusammengenäht sind.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
